      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "GO GO SPIRIT (6) turned in a plain performance last time when seventh at Bulli over 400m behind Hard Style Girl (23.29) in a Grade 4/5. Placed at his previous run. Still to record a win from this draw but has never missed the frame in three starts. Should be very hard to beat this time. EXEMPLARY (2) is a well performed dog and winner of nine races who is worth forgiving after finishing out of the placings at this track (23.42). Solid record here at this trip including two wins. The form out of last race has been strong. Key runner who gets his chance to atone. DIRE (1) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Better run when finding the frame last time though, finishing second (18.29) at this track. Form at the trip sound including five wins. Will give a great sight again. MISS GOLDIE (3) looks a top-three chance while fresh.",
